title: Against Tyranny!
author: Daonon
pages:
#- This is a message to all citizens of devoted - citizens toiling under the rule of capitalists, of kings, of oligarchies. We call for you to look at what you want, and what those around you want, and then look at what fate has been forced upon you by those
#- so-called leaders. Destroy the systems that oppress you and in their place create community. The division between race, gender, sexuality, is created by the ruling class to keep you from rising up. We call for destruction, yes, but we also call for the
#- creation of community. There is nothing stoppping you, the worker, from claiming the means of production. There is nothing stopping you from refusing to fight in wars between nations that have nothing to do with you. There are more resources in this world
#- than can be used by all of us. To every bullying nation that destroys or imposes its will on real communities, to every supposedly "benevolent" king or "benevolent" capitalist, to every insufferable 4chan bore, we say one thing and one thing only...
#- FUCK OFF!
#- 